	<ThingDef ParentName="GW_AM_BolterBase">
        <defName>GW_AM_Gun_BoltPistol</defName>
        <label>Bolt Pistol</label>
        <description>In the expansive tapestry of the Warhammer 40,000 universe, the Bolt Pistol, a formidable sidearm, emerges as a symbol of lethal precision and close-quarters firepower within the arsenal of the Space Marines. This compact yet potent weapon is crafted with a matte-black ceramite alloy, ensuring durability amidst the grim and relentless nature of the galactic battlefield.\n\nThe Bolt Pistol operates as a rapid-firing, self-loading, and magazine-fed firearm, unleashing mass-reactive bolts or projectiles with every precise shot. These explosive bolts, possessing destructive potential upon impact, prove effective against a diverse array of adversaries, showcasing the versatility required in the Space Marine's relentless combat engagements.\n\nFunctioning as a hybrid weapon, the Bolt Pistol seamlessly bridges the gap between conventional sidearms and small-scale artillery. Its deadly accuracy, impactful shots, and rapid firing rate make it a fearsome asset, delivering devastating salvos while maintaining precision in the chaos of close to mid-range combat.\n\nWielding the Bolt Pistol, the Space Marines epitomize the unmatched might and cutting-edge technology of the Imperium of Man, showcasing their unwavering resolve in the eternal struggle against the countless threats that plague the war-ravaged galaxy of Warhammer 40,000.</description>
